NEW ON FASTCOMPANY.COM: Battle Plan
-----------------------------------------------------

Battle Plan | by Anni Layne Rodgers
Former Army lieutenant colonel Ralph Peters outlines
nine strategies for understanding, fighting, and
defeating the new enemy. Rule #1: Culture is king.
http://robin.fastcompany.com/cgi-bin/nph-t.pl?U=1781&M=79151&MS=3242

Good Work | by Polly LaBarre
An important new book testifies to the power of
professional excellence and to the challenges of
meeting social commitments in the face of fierce
marketplace pressures. Can you pass the "mirror test" ?
http://robin.fastcompany.com/cgi-bin/nph-t.pl?U=1782&M=79151&MS=3242

Who's Fast Spotlight: Bob Moffat | by Charles Fishman
Bob Moffat has one of the more thankless big jobs in an
industry ruled by price wars, vanishing stock prices,
consolidations, and layoffs. So why is Moffat, head of
IBM's PC group, having such a good time at work?
http://robin.fastcompany.com/cgi-bin/nph-t.pl?U=1783&M=79151&MS=3242

